ActFirst Nations Fiscal and Statistical Management Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Schedule to the First Nations Fiscal and Statistical Management Act
PrecisORDER AMENDING THE SCHEDULE TO THE FIRST NATIONS FISCAL AND STATISTICAL MANAGEMENT ACT to add 3 First Nations (Beaver Lake Cree Nation (AB); Gitsegukla First Nation (BC); Kahkewistahaw First Nation (SK)) to the Schedule allowing them to participate in the property tax regime established by the FIRST NATIONS FISCAL AND STATISTICAL MANAGEMENT ACT.
